description: Creates a vehicle model (model manifest) that specifies signals (attributes, branches, sensors, and actuators). For more information, see Vehicle models in the Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise Developer Guide.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the vehicle model to create.

parameters.name: nodes
parameters.description: A list of nodes, which are a general abstraction of signals. (string) ---

parameters.name: signalCatalogArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of a signal catalog.

parameters.name: tags
parameters.description: Metadata that can be used to manage the vehicle model. (dict) --- A set of key/value pairs that are used to manage the resource. The tag's key. The tag's value.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the created vehicle model.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the created vehicle model.
